>                                                   easier to remember.
>                                 For example, for dropping with
>                                                   seqlevels<-, the user
>                                                   needs
>                                                   to remember that
>                                 "force" is necessary to drop. Much
>                                                   easier to just say
>                                                   "dropSeqlevels(),
