>
>                         because
>
>                                               the code was
>                                               developed independently,
>                                 support for different objects
>
>                 was
>
>                                               inconsistent. So
>                                               actually, yes, the
>                                 maintenance (and use) burden for the
>                                               previous state of
>                                               affairs was substantial.
